## 封装加载图片的promise  
```js
let loadImg = (src)=>{
    return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
        // write your code here
    })
}
```

student_answer:
let loadImg = (src)=>{
    return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
        // write your code here
       let image=new img()
       image.onload=()=>{
      		resolve(image)
       }
      	image.onerror=()=>{
          reject(new Error("error"+src))
        }
       image.src=src;
    })
}
